{"tid":1161095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗：探索在人手嚴重不足行業引入外勞","createTime":"2019-05-19T02:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T03:01:03.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"631d2b4247a25d4d7d2c006cbc90979221736ab0","tid":1161095,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/CS-BLOG-190519-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FCS-BLOG-190519-10.jpg&h=fe6e0fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政府最新人力資源推算預計，到2027年出現人力短缺近17萬人。政務司司長張建宗表示，政府會適度針對人手嚴重不足的行業認真探索，在香港以外地方引入人力。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗發表網誌表示，隨着本港人口高齡化及勞動人口萎縮的趨勢，對本港經濟增長和長遠發展將造成一定的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n在人力資源規劃委員會上，不少專家、學者都認為長期人力短缺可能拖慢經濟發展的勢頭，因此要做好人力規劃，全方位釋放本地勞動力。<br />\n<br />\n由婦女、少數族裔、新來港人士、殘疾人士，以至有意重投就業市場的退休人士，對補足勞動力可說是一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，政府會適度針對人手嚴重不足的行業認真探索，在香港以外地方引入人力。"},{"pid":"1263005ba58a51a035979be845f951c4a134cdce","tid":1161095,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:36:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=348496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348496&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPdnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=5a645a2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348496&h=7d6fd73e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=348496</a>"},{"pid":"cab395c6617f368112d0848a6d5eb82b191e55b4","tid":1161095,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:39:13.000Z","msg":"有料怕咩競爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794746a42954ddf5c205f83adcb659cc3ee4862d","tid":1161095,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:42:23.000Z